snippet.title: Mistfall Hunter - Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Mistfall Hunter is a third-person action PvPvE extraction RPG, set in the aftermath of Ragnarok, a conflict that nearly led to the extinction of the gods. Team up with friends, combine your strengths, and carve your path through dangerous monsters and rival players.

Prepare to hunt hidden treasures, but beware the golden mist that ensnares the unwary. 
Only those who are brave enough to face the challenges will emerge unscathed from its merciless grasp.

Mistfall Hunter is now available for your wishlist on Xbox and Steam. 

Visit our official website https://mistfallhunter.com to register for the upcoming PC beta test coming later this year. 

Check Mistfall Hunter in Xbox and Steam stores: 
Xbox: https://www.microsoft.com/store/productid/9pn5wjm7v6m0
Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/3282300
Contacts: support@mail.mistfallhunter.com

Follow our official Discord: 
https://discord.gg/tZPffZ7X

#mistfallhunter #xbox  #steam
